'''Afaha Efiat''' is a village in [[Etinan]] local government area of [[Akwa Ibom State]], [[Nigeria]].<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com.ng/books?id=SDKlJQBZ92IC&q=Afaha+Efiat|title=National Gazetteer of Place Names: Cross River State|date=1985|publisher=National Population Bureau, Demographic Division|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com.ng/books?id=32knAQAAIAAJ&q=Afaha+Efiat&dq=Afaha+Efiat|title=Cross River and Akwa Ibom State Population Bulletin 1983-90: 1963 Population of Cross River and Akwa Ibom State|date=1985|publisher=Statistics Division, Ministry of Finance & Economic Planning|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com.ng/books?id=57_hAAAAMAAJ&q=Afaha+Efiat&dq=Afaha+Efiat|title=Newswatch|date=1998|publisher=Newswatch Communications Limited|language=en}}</ref>
