'''''El simulacro: Por qué el Kirchnerismo es reaccionario''''' ({{lang-es|The deception. The reasons why Kirchnerism is conservative}}) is a 2013 Argentine book by [[Alejandro Katz]]. It describes the policies of the governments or [[Néstor Kirchner]] and [[Cristina Fernández de Kirchner]] and the way the government propaganda network describes it.<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.revistaenie.clarin.com/ideas/politica-economia/Diseccion-kirchnerismo_0_984501565.html|title= Disección del kirchnerismo |trans-title=Dissection of Kirchnerism|language= Spanish|author= Adolfo Coronato|date= September 5, 2013|publisher= Clarín|accessdate=October 29, 2014}}</ref>

