'''Ras Kasar''' is a [[Cape (geography)|cape]] in northeastern [[Africa]], on the border between [[Eritrea]] and [[Sudan]] at the [[Red Sea]]. It is the northernmost point in Eritrea and the easternmost point in Sudan.

