{{Infobox lake | name = Tyresö-Flaten | image = Tyresö-Flaten, 2007-06-25, Lillsjön part of lake viewed from bridge.jpeg | caption = Western end of the lake | image_bathymetry = | caption_bathymetry = | coords = {{coord|59|13|17.9|N|18|15|41.2|E|region:SE_type:waterbody_scale:10000|display=inline,title}} | type = | inflow = [[Långsjön, Skälsätra-Tutviken|Långsjön]], [[Barnsjön]] | outflow = [[Albysjön, Tyresö|Albysjön]] | catchment = | basin_countries = Sweden | length = | width = | area = {{convert|36.0|ha|abbr=on}}<ref name="SöEko"/> | depth = | max-depth = {{convert|26|m|abbr=on}} | volume = | residence_time = | shore = | elevation = {{convert|19|m|abbr=on}}<ref name="SöEko" /> | cities = [[Tyresö]] | reference = <ref name="SöEko">Södertörnsekologerna</ref><ref name="Tyresö">Tyresö Municipality, ''Tyresåns sjösystem''</ref> }} [[File:Gammelströmmen, Tyresö, 2007-06-25, inlet of Tyresö-Flaten.jpeg|thumb|Gammelströmmen. the inflow of lake Tyresö-Flaten.]] '''Tyresö-Flaten''' is a [[lake]] in [[Tyresö Municipality]], south of [[Stockholm]], [[Sweden]].
The lake forms part of the [[Tyresån Lake System]] and as such is considered important for recreational activities such as angling and bathing.<ref name="Tyresö" /> Common fish species include [[European perch|Perch]], [[Zander]] [[Northern pike|Pike]], [[Trout|Lake trout]]<!--- Insjööring --->, [[Carp Bream]], and [[Rutilus|Roach]].<ref name="Tyresö-fish">Tyresö Municipality, ''Fiske''</ref>
== Environmental impact == When water stagnate in late summer [[hydrogen sulfide]] and oxygen shortage occurs in lake sediments. However, level of bacteria are low and the lake is considered safe for bathing. No contaminations except nutritive salt have been reported.<ref name="Tyresö" />
