===Presidency pro tempore===
{{main article|President pro tempore of the Union of South American Nations}}

[[File:Evo_Morales_2011.jpg|thumb|upright|[[Evo Morales]], the current [[President pro tempore of the Union of South American Nations|President of UNASUR]].]]
The temporary presidency will be governed by a year and will be rotating among the member countries between each UNASUR meeting. According to the document "Decisions of the Political Dialogue", which was signed during the 1st South American Energy Meeting, a permanent general cabinet will be created and headquartered in [[Quito]], Ecuador.<ref name = "Secretary-General2">{{Cite web|url = http://www.unasursg.org/node/4|title = Presidency Pro Tempore|publisher = Unasul|accessdate = 5 December 2014}}</ref>

